snippet.title: Monkey Splash!! Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Monkey Splash!! is out now! It's officially time to SPLASH!!

Monkey Splash!! is an arcade, action-platformer featuring monkeys, diving, and historical landmarks! Fire your funky monkey up these colossal structures, avoiding rivals along the way to achieve the ultimate dive!

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2353950/Monkey_Splash/
